The,AT,T,Speech,API,powered,by,the,AT,T,WATSON,speech,engine,allows,developers,to,add,speech,transcription,to,their,apps,Users,send,audio,and,text,is,returned,With,the,API,developers,can,create,apps,that,run,on,any,device,and,cellular,network,in,the,US,The,cross,carrier,Speech,API,transcribes,a,spoken,word,audio,file,to,text,It,also,takes,into,consideration,spoken,context,such,as,searching,for,a,TV,show,The,Speech,API,is,optimized,and,tuned,for,specific,contexts,including,Web,Search,Business,Search,Voicemail,SMS,Question,and,Answer,TV,and,Generic,The,API,uses,REST,protocols,and,XML,JSON,data,formats